name: INSetRadioStationIntentHandling
desc: The handler interface for changing a radio station.DeprecatedThis intent is no longer available. You may define a custom intent instead. For more information, see Deprecated SiriKit Intent Domains.

items.name: func resolveStationName(for: INSetRadioStationIntent, with: (INStringResolutionResult) -> Void)
items.desc: Resolves the name of the radio station.

items.name: func resolveChannel(for: INSetRadioStationIntent, with: (INStringResolutionResult) -> Void)
items.desc: Resolves the channel number for the radio station.

items.name: func resolvePresetNumber(for: INSetRadioStationIntent, with: (INIntegerResolutionResult) -> Void)
items.desc: Resolves the preset number used to select the radio station.

items.name: func confirm(intent: INSetRadioStationIntent, completion: (INSetRadioStationIntentResponse) -> Void)
items.desc: Confirms whether you can change the radio station.
